=======================
Mail Format with Parent
=======================

Use name of parent for mailing if partner has no name.

For a detailed documentation have a look at https://www.odoo-wiki.org/mail-format-with-parent.html

Configuration
~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* No additional configurations needed

